      "updated": 1784302058742,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1  Agent → /mcp/ with Bearer ctdl_\n2  citadel_search tool → FastAPI\n3  Resolve read scope (ADR-0009):\n     own seat node + Central only\n4  Cognee: pgvector similarity\n     + Kuzu graph expansion\n5  Fail-closed visibility filter\n     (_content_visible_ids)\n6  Return: presence for all seats,\n     content only for the caller",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1  Agent → /mcp/ with Bearer ctdl_\n2  citadel_search tool → FastAPI\n3  Resolve read scope (ADR-0009):\n     own seat node + Central only\n4  Cognee: pgvector similarity\n     + Kuzu graph expansion\n5  Fail-closed visibility filter\n     (_content_visible_ids)\n6  Return: presence for all seats,\n     content only for the caller",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
