      "text": "1  Scheduler wakes (opt-in flag)\n2  Phase 1 subprocess (add-only):\n     github → repo → self-improve\n     → promotion → linear\n3  Web holds writer_lock; cognify\n     suppressed during Phase 1\n4  Subprocess exits → frees Kuzu lock\n5  Phase 2 in-loop: cognify(force),\n     web = sole Kuzu writer\n6  Verify canary → _LAST_CANARY\n     → gates /readyz",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1  Scheduler wakes (opt-in flag)\n2  Phase 1 subprocess (add-only):\n     github → repo → self-improve\n     → promotion → linear\n3  Web holds writer_lock; cognify\n     suppressed during Phase 1\n4  Subprocess exits → frees Kuzu lock\n5  Phase 2 in-loop: cognify(force),\n     web = sole Kuzu writer\n6  Verify canary → _LAST_CANARY\n     → gates /readyz",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
