      "updated": 1784302058752,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "⚠  SINGLE EVENT LOOP — Cognee binds its async DB engine to the first event loop that touches it.\nAll cognee work (add / cognify / query) must run on the web’s long-lived loop (scripts/stage_loop.py = one shared asyncio.Runner). A fresh asyncio.run() raises “Future attached to a different loop”.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "vlhKTNtO_252f0YVHZozU",
      "originalText": "⚠  SINGLE EVENT LOOP — Cognee binds its async DB engine to the first event loop that touches it.\nAll cognee work (add / cognify / query) must run on the web’s long-lived loop (scripts/stage_loop.py = one shared asyncio.Runner). A fresh asyncio.run() raises “Future attached to a different loop”.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
